      <title>欧洲央行穆勒称通胀放缓的信心正在增强</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/ecb-s-muller-says-confidence-growing-that-inflation-is-slowing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行管理委员会委员马迪斯·穆勒在一份书面声明中表示，整个欧元区的通胀势头正在放缓，人们越来越相信通胀将成为过去。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-13/ecb-s-muller-says-confidence-growing-that-inflation-is-slowing</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Sep 2024 08:02:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
